These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, animation
3 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the owner of the mouse##7
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | documentary |
| Pet           | mouse  | hamster     | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, pop
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, roller, car
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person driving the roller##7
3. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | folk | pop |
| Transport     | roller       | car     | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, 7up
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, trike
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person driving the scooter##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | fanta | tea | 7up  |
| Transport   | trike  | helicopter  | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, police-officer, entrepreneur
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, animation, documentary
1. the security-guard is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the police-officer##7
2. the person watching animation movies is not the security-guard##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | police-officer | security-guard | entrepreneur     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | crime          | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, ambient, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, jet-ski
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the fan of ambient##7
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | classical      | soul     | ambient   |
| Transport     | jet-ski | snowmobile | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, classical, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: german, canadian, chinese
1. the german is on the left or right of the canadian##3
2. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the chinese and the fan of rock##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | classical     | rock     |
| Nationality   | chinese | canadian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is soccer##7
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | hamster       | mouse      | horse       |
| Sport   | soccer | handball | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, firefighter, architect
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, animation, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the writer##3
2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the firefighter##7
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | architect | writer  | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel      | spy | animation      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, board-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, chef, journalist
1. the journalist is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
2. the chef is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the project-manager is somewhere between the chef and the person who's hobby is cooking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | cooking | board-games | collecting   |
| Job     | journalist    | project-manager  | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, handball
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is swimming##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | juice   | iced-tea    | 7up |
| Sport      | handball | surfing | swimming |

