.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, camping, hiking
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indian, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the indian and the chinese##7
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the chinese is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | hiking | cooking | camping |
| Nationality   | indian    | mexican    | chinese         |

