.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, tomato, pineapple
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, spy, family
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person eating cherry##7
3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | cherry  | pineapple       | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | spy |

