.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, metal, salsa
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the fan of pop and the fan of salsa##7
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of metal is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person drinking milk##7
4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | fanta | milk |
| Music-Genre   | pop | metal    | salsa |

