.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, taxi, van
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
2. the person driving the van is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person eating cauliflower##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | grapefruit | pineapple | cauliflower |
| Transport   | van  | taxi       | bus      |

