The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, handball, surfing
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the person who's sport is handball##7
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | goat  | chinchilla       | ferret    |
| Sport   | rowing | surfing | handball |

