.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pomegranate, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: american, german, dutch
1. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
2. the person eating zucchini is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the dutch and the american##7
4. the american is the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | zucchini | pomegranate     | cherry   |
| Nationality   | dutch   | german | american |

