.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, scientist, coach
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the scientist##7
3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | water     | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | coach | lawyer | scientist    |

 